  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5346596">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5346596/" class="title-link">名副其实</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5346596"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2874642/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2874642-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2874642/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">小隐</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-03-15"
      class="main-meta">2012-03-15 19:51:53</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5346596_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  很讨厌时下那些吹得花好稻好的书 连书名都只是一个勾引消费者的噱头 是的 勾引 而且还是针对“消费者” 而不是“读者” 他们只贪图速食 连书也买快餐书  发完牢骚 说回这本书 以前没听过这作者 在听二王讲座的时候 瓜突然摸出来送我 还觉得莫名其妙 挺反感打着启蒙旗号的弱智二...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5346596_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5346596_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










